@{i}1.8@{ui}	- The @{"ROMTag check" LINK TagTest} added.
@{i}1.7@{ui}	- The @{"library check" LINK LibTest} is new. Option -l.
@{i}1.6@{ui}	- Option -i added for additional @{"softinterrupt Test" LINK SoftRupts}.
@{i}1.5.6@{ui}	- Option -e added for additional @{"exec.library test" LINK ExecTest}.
