@{i}1.5.3@{ui}	- Cache remover ready and option -d "knows" the Dos-cache.
@{i}1.5.2@{ui}	- @{"DOS-test" LINK DosTest} and DOS-cache improved for OS2.0
@{i}1.5.1@{ui}	- Show in what mode a file was opened in the cache.
